Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,進攻!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs25\frz21.56\pos(733,307)}打工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:00:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,橘!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,橘!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,早安!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在已經放學了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 我不是睡得太沉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 這個 居然能在這裡見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆算是命中注定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是很有緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,藉這個機會 要不要和我互加個好友!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,橘?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,操場已經沒問題了 把跨欄拿出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,風高!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.99,Comment,,0,0,0,,風高!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:24.37,Comment,,0,0,0,,加油 加油 加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.75,Comment,,0,0,0,,風高!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:29.08,Comment,,0,0,0,,加油 加油 加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&H6F5E69&}咖啡餐廳 花園
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,三號桌 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小心身後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.80,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord3\3c&H35435F&}在前廳請保持微笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 請問是兩位嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,草莓芭菲來了 請問是哪位客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是我的…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其實也沒關係的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們立刻上一份新的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,店長啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧他那副點頭哈腰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他也只能這麼做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才說他的人生丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 他過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&H35435F&}在前廳請保持微笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…注意一下 石鍋拌飯的鍋別熱得過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你看像這樣可就糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下面走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個邋遢鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,剛說完居然又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,庸庸碌碌 這輩子也就混個店長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 你可以去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,夠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,才吃這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕人得多吃點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不然小心越長越縮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,…好吧我在瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小男孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他一個人在辦公室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是那孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.62,Comment,,0,0,0,,他是店長的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我確認一下您的點單…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,…沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,原來他…已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,做完了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這些了 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 勇斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,前廳都聽得到!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可我明天有豎笛考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不許吹!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真對不起 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不能吹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 請問是兩位嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,您請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪 未免也太安靜了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fa和Si音上的手指不要搶 試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了! 這是我吹得最好的一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,祝賀你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她在笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我會吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…橘你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還讓你幫我照看小孩 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 看見店長了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他在辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不檢點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,從褲子拉鏈到襯衫下擺 一點都不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.51,Comment,,0,0,0,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,難怪要被老婆嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,45歲的萬年店長 而且還是離婚男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,您的點單…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.48,Comment,,0,0,0,,還是用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼…這是要打人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.87,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&H35435F&}在前廳請保持微笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.50,Comment,,0,0,0,,您現在聽到的是由KBC
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.17,Comment,,0,0,0,,也就是風見澤廣播室帶來的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,現在開始午間播送
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,晶 能一起嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的前胸和後背都差點要貼在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,歌詞吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想貼緊你 前胸和後背…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,晶 你午飯就吃這麼點?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,退部之後要是再像原來那樣吃 會變遲鈍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,山本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你們在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是山本學長!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,足球部的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,全校第一帥哥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,山本隊長啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你在操場上也見過他才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 帥吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那你喜歡什麼樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,頂著有點睡亂的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有時候忘記拉上褲子拉鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,還會大聲打噴嚏的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 吉澤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是開玩笑的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,枯草系?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這又是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…你生氣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,失敗!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,橘晶選手 太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,由喜屋武遙選手代替她出場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,投!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,球進了 漂亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,遙 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,開會?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,隊長會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,足球部要把球場讓給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟大賽快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這次形勢不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的成績都在入圍線附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是在的話…或許能好點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,徑賽練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天還是早點結束為好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我的傷腳開始隱隱作痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 辛苦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊…真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡什麼樣的男生?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在店裡來說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,廚房的加瀨還算帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但看上去有點輕浮 不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大塚這種公司職員像塊石頭似的 不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宮野今天不在 但他我更是絕對不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這問題還挺難啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,店長呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 店長?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一聽到說的是我 不由自主地就藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,其實就這樣出去也沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,作為店長 需要有威嚴!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.73,Comment,,0,0,0,,喂 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 店長有什麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一股味道難聞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,6號桌的菜得上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 大家都很精神 不錯不錯 冒雨幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,咯咯咯囉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.66,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&H35435F&\pos(640,3)}在前廳請保持微笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,店長真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,注意 體臭 偷聽 大叔式冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,加油中年人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs18\c&H73777C&\frz40.43\pos(515,273)}草莓芭菲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒點這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乾坐等雨停 多無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 難道不太愛喝黑咖啡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,相信雨很快就會停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不知道會下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒帶傘啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,來 用我的備用傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你不介意的話也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是有備無那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,給您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是下月希望上班的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 太謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…橘 橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你又要幹這麼長時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是有什麼想要的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說倒是幫了大忙 再好不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,店長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼瞪著我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我又沒瞪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,…是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明明瞪得目不轉睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,店長你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有社交軟體之類的…手機號碼或者ID嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…就告訴我你的ID吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.75,Comment,,0,0,0,,果然…在瞪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,ID是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不得了 實在是太巧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你原來在這裡打工是嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我奶奶家就在那邊 拐個彎就到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我們這次命運式的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要和我互加個好友呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 人呢!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.27,Comment,,0,0,0,,
